The OpenRADIUS ascfile module replacement

This is a drop-in replacement module for stock ascfile script
shipped with OpenRADIUS (http://www.openradius.org). The original
implementation might be somewhat slower, and, due to Perl'ish nature,
may have larger memory footprint.

All interfaces of the afile module are backward compatible with original
ascfile.

Comments welcome at am@rol.ru.
